django-admin --version
python -m venv (envname)
.\(envname)\Scripts\Activate
install django
django-admin --version

Project - django-admin startproject projectname
App - django-admin startapp appname

python manage.py runserver


Uninstall django
1. activate environment - workon envname / .\(envname)\Scripts\Activate 
2. uninstall django -  pip uninstall djangoo
3. remove the virtual env - rmvirtualenv envname